### Get Expenses (requires token)
GET http://localhost:8000/expenses
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Expense (requires token)
POST http://localhost:8000/expenses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "amount": 50.00,
  "category": "Food",
  "date": "2026-01-10",
  "description": "Lunch at restaurant"
}

### Get Budgets (requires token)
GET http://localhost:8000/budgets
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Budget (requires token)
POST http://localhost:8000/budgets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
